      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite covering hemolysis-relevant flow regimes; formal change-control process in place.",
      "rationale": "Solver is version-controlled and a regression test suite exists, but the test suite does not cover rotating-frame hemolysis-relevant regimes. Change-control documentation is informal. Achieved Gradation 2 against required Gradation 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
